didn't know how to write a single line of code. But marketing always

00:00:22.820 --> 00:00:28.490
works with sales, and that's how I got started with Salesforce. And just due

00:00:28.490 --> 00:00:31.460
to you know, circumstances on the job, I dabbled a little in code

00:00:31.460 --> 00:00:35.050
and, and I fell in love. It was, it was love at first sight.

